'''臭氧化锂'''，化学式为LiO<sub>3</sub>，这种物质目前还没制备出纯品，只制得了四[[氨|氨]]合臭氧化锂（LiO<sub>3</sub>·4NH<sub>3</sub>），这种四氨合物可以和硫酸反应，生成硫酸盐并放出[[氧气|氧气]]。<ref>{{cite journal|journal=Inorganic Chemistry|volume=1|issue=3|language=en|issn=0020-1669|date=1962-8|pages=659–661|doi=10.1021/ic50003a041|url=http://pubs.acs.org/doi/abs/10.1021/ic50003a041|title=Preparation and Properties of Lithium Ozonide and the Use of Ammonia in the Preparation of Ozonides|accessdate=2019-05-24|author=Andrew J. Kacmarek, John M. McDonough, Irvine J. Solomon}}</ref>该物质不稳定的原因可能是[[锂|锂]]离子的半径与[[臭氧根|臭氧根]]离子相差过大。<ref name="无机化学丛书">{{cite book|title=《无机化学丛书》第一卷：稀有气体、氢、碱金属|pages=P322|author=张青莲|isbn=7-03-002238-6|location=北京|publisher=科学出版社|date=1991年11月}}</ref>臭氧化锂的推测晶胞参数为a=3.053，b=4.931，c=5.197。<ref>{{cite journal|journal=Journal of Structural Chemistry|volume=51|issue=6|language=en|issn=0022-4766|date=2010-12|pages=1005–1013|doi=10.1007/s10947-010-0157-1|url=http://link.springer.com/10.1007/s10947-010-0157-1|title=Structure, mechanical stability, and chemical bond in alkali metal oxides|accessdate=2019-05-24|author=Yu. N. Zhuravlev, O. S. Obolonskaya}}</ref>有文献指出如果纯品能够制得，它可以用作高氧含量的供氧源。<ref>Petrocelli A W, Capotosto A. The Synthesis and Utilization of Low Molecular Weight Ozonides for Air Revitalization Purposes （[https://ntrs.nasa.gov/archive/nasa/casi.ntrs.nasa.gov/19650001419.pdf PDF] {{Wayback|url=https://ntrs.nasa.gov/archive/nasa/casi.ntrs.nasa.gov/19650001419.pdf |date=20170503203132 }}）. National Aeronautics and Space Administration, 1964.</ref>

